接口 TimeBarIntervalFilter

  • 所有超级接口:

    AbstractTimeBarIntervalFilter

    public interface TimeBarIntervalFilter
extends de.jaret.util.misc.PropertyObservable
    Filter for intervals in a TimeBarViewer. If set on a timebar viewer only those intervals will be displayed that are selected by the filter to be in the result.
    版本:
    $Id: TimeBarIntervalFilter.java 800 2008-12-27 22:27:33Z kliem $
